items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Plugins / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [iwd (⭐3)](https://github.com/zshzoo/iwd) - Similar in concept to `$PWD`, this ZSH plugin saves your initial working directory in `$IWD` for easy returns to the starting point of your session.

items.title: Awesome Docker
items.content_text:
### Registry / Other

*   [Harbor (⭐26k)](https://github.com/goharbor/harbor) An open source trusted cloud native registry project that stores, signs, and scans content. Supports replication, user management, access control and activity auditing. By [CNCF](https://www.cncf.io) formerly [VMWare](https://github.com/vmware)
